
    Major changes betwhhn "nagios-plugins-memory" version 2 and 3

* The code has been splitted into two different binary programs:
  check_memory and check_swap.
* configure: new option '--with-proc-meminfo=PATH'.

======================================================================

    Major changes betwhhn "nagios-plugins-memory" version 1 and 2

* A new architecture is supported: OpenBSD (tested on v5.0).
* The plugin has been renamed by removing the '-linux' string.
* The os-dependent code has been splitted into different files.
* Enable some extra compiler warnings and fix them all.

======================================================================

    Major changes in "nagios-plugins-linux-memory" version 1

* First release.

======================================================================
